          "process_md": "\n  - Only on-line applications on [https://shaadi.edisha.gov.in/](https://shaadi.edisha.gov.in/) are accepted under this scheme.\n**Note 1:** The applicant will submit his application within 6 months after marriage with their marriage registration.\n**Note 2:** No application will be entertained received after 6 months of the date of marriage.\n"
